      <h2 class="section__heading">A Certified ProAdvisor takes the call &mdash; not a call center.</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>The reason to talk to a ProAdvisor rather than general support is simple: the person on the line has been tested on QuickBooks and works inside real client files every day. At TechBrot a Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor with active Online and Desktop certifications takes the call, listens to what&rsquo;s actually happening in your file, and tells you honestly whether there&rsquo;s work to do, what it would take, and whether part of your problem belongs with Intuit instead. Any work is scoped in writing before it begins. Independent firm &mdash; not Intuit, and not Intuit&rsquo;s ProAdvisor referral line; an Intuit account, login, or billing matter stays with Intuit.</p>
